Ed Goes Outside putting one foot in front of the other

Running

Long distance running shapes a significant part of who I am and what I do in my free time. I love to go on lengthy and wild trail runs as means to get ultimate consciousness of my natural surroundings. It's my vehicle for finding inner peace and overcoming my existential dread.

Adventures

I am fascinated with long distance, self-powered travel. I enjoy the simplicity of carrying everything I need on my pack, and the liberating feeling one gets walking for days at a time.
